        <div class="T__wrap">
            <div class="layout-6">
                <img src="images/work4/material1.jpg" alt="IMG">
                <p><em>Life Jacket Material<br>
                ---nylon fabric or neoprene<br>
                (NEOPRENE)</em><br><br>
                Reuse of waste materials.<br>
                Life jackets are waterproof, relatively strong material,  more durable.</p>
